{"tid":2024935,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"何栢良：在沙灘酒吧除口罩風險較戴口罩遊行聚集高","createTime":"2020-05-20T02:26:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T02:29:57.000Z","uid":60281,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cf2c850a96c702779c19039e16698743da941f28","tid":2024935,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T02:26:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1288757&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1288757%26csid%3D261_341&d=Vmg9VhgMmKCDk1oLDtgP7pX8N1KgQotyuydbLhb69C0%3D&h=6d7c6b0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1288757&amp;csid=261_341</a><br />\n<br />\n港大感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良在本台節目表示，市民到沙灘或酒吧等地方除口罩，感染風險較戴口罩參與遊行聚集高，認為政府防疫措施需要有一致性，不能重開部分風險高地方的同時，在低風險地區繼續實施限制。何栢良指，近日酒吧在周末人頭湧湧，外傭亦有聚集，認為當局需要做好管理，不應「睜一隻眼，閉一隻眼」，又強調政府要強制市民在公共交通等高危地方戴口罩。"},{"pid":"9cf50c28230fe08f33b91ac91bb25b4ee6f16bb7","tid":2024935,"uid":259812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T02:28:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63abfa5ded0a145dc8d5f6b83b12cf20e73568ac","tid":2024935,"uid":89754,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T02:29:57.000Z","msg":"直插777<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}